latestIgtvVideos.title: Create a new look by Old outfits🙈
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Don’t wanna repeat same outfits?Can’t buy new clothes?
And Festive season is around so what to do?
Solution: mix match your old outfits and create a whole new look!

Look 1 
Mixed & matched the Choli of my Gharara set with a different lehenga 

Look 2 
Mixed matched the Gharara and its dupatta with the top of my night suit.

Look 3 
Mixed matched the blouse of a south Indian saree with a different lehenga and turned it into a crop top n skirt 

Look 4
Mixed matched the blouse n dupatta of the lehenga set with mumma’s saree and tadaaaa!!

Look 5
Every girl has a sports bra so why just use it for exercising 
Team it with any matching saree and there is your new look! 

@popxofashion @plixxo
